Café Drink Station\n<c=@flavor>Provides drinks for delivery to café customers.</c>
Café Transporter\n<c=@flavor>When this decoration is placed, café customers will enter and exit from it instead of from the waypoint.</c>
Café Chair\n<c=@flavor>Café customers will sit here to order! Note that customers will have difficulty reaching seats high off the ground.</c>
Café Food Station\n<c=@flavor>Provides food to deliver to café customers.</c>
Café Souvenir Station\n<c=@flavor>Provides trinkets to deliver to café customers.</c>
Café Console\n<c=@flavor>Handles testing, opening, and upgrades for your café.</c>
Café Guide Beacon\n<c=@flavor>Café customers will follow beacons to avoid obstacles on the way to seating.</c>
